    "melinoe-intro":{
        "dialogue" : [
            {"text":"Artemis?! What are you doing here? This is a very dangerous place.",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"This forest is not a normal forest; it's full of creatures that will try to finish off anyone who enters.",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"You ask why I'm here?",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"The forest is full of magical objects with powers; I'm trying to discover their origin.",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"However, every time I manage to leave with a few, they turn into coins.",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"Further ahead is the place where I set up camp. How about you continue and I'll show you.",
             "options": [1]}
        ],
        "speed" : 1,
        "npcName" : "Melinoe", "portrait":"Melinoe",
        "userOptions" : [
            {
                "label" : "Next",
                "event" : "NEXT_PAGE",
                "color" : "Green"
            },
            {
                "label" : "Exit",
                "event" : "END",
                "color" : "Red"
            }
        ]
    },
    "melinoe-hub-intro":{
        "dialogue" : [
            {"text":"Welcome to my humble shop. Here I keep interesting magical items that might be useful to you.",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"But I'm not foolish, I will only give them to you in exchange for some coins hehe.",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"I see you have nothing... Earlier I saw a slime ahead. Kill it and take the items it drops.",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"When you return they will turn into coins that you can use to trade with me.",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"How do you not know how to shoot?! You are the goddess of the hunt, you always carry a bow!",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"Anyway, to draw the bow, hold the click and drag the mouse in the opposite direction to where you're aiming.",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"When you release the click the arrow will be fired in that direction.",
             "options": [0]},
            {"text":"So what are you waiting for. Off on an adventure!",
             "options": [1]}
        ],
        "speed" : 1,
        "npcName" : "Melinoe", "portrait":"Melinoe",
        "userOptions" : [
